name: Super Ultra Star Shooter
overview: Shooting stars and getting burgers! You are Vau Woah, an intergalactic fighter pilot and freelance hero! A distress signal from a dangerous planet filled with deadly aliens has been sent out and only Vau Woah can help! However, it's lunch time, and a good hero never rescues on an empty stomach! Time for Vau to start his intergalactic quest for lunch! Travel an endless amount of levels! Collect power-ups to defeat enemy ships! Get burgers and fries! Try to get the highest score possible!
